Usage

generate_graduation_submission_file(
  input_df = usheUtils::fake_graduation_df,
  with_intermediates = FALSE
)

Arguments

input_df

A Data Frame. Must contain the following data fields: (student_id, ssn, last_name, first_name, middle_name, name_suffix, first_admit_state_code, first_admit_county_code, first_admit_country_iso_code, birth_date, gender_code, is_hispanic_latino_ethnicity, is_asian, is_black, is_american_indian_alaskan, is_hawaiian_pacific_islander, is_white, is_international, is_other_race, graduation_date, primary_major_cip_code, degree_id, degree_status_code, cumulative_graduation_gpa, transfer_cumulative_credits_earned, total_cumulative_ap_credits_earned, total_cumulative_clep_credits_earned, overall_cumulative_credits_earned, total_remedial_hours, total_cumulative_credits_attempted_other_sources, level_id, previous_degree_type, ipeds_award_level_code, required_credits, high_school_code, ssid, earned_contact_hrs , program_hrs, graduated_term_id, financial_aid_year_id, season, college_desc, primary_major_desc, degree_desc)

with_intermediates

Boolean: Option to include intermediate calculated fields.

Value

A Data Frame, with all of the USHE elements required for upload submission. This will also include intermediate values, used to calculate USHE data elements, if option is set.
